Sure, here are five example sentences in Serbian that use the word "roku" in different forms and positions, with translations in English:

1. Molim vas da mi prebacite novac na *račun u roku* od tri dana. (Please transfer the money to my account within three days.)
2. Želim da *rokujem* sa prodavcem oko cene ovog automobila. (I want to negotiate with the seller about the price of this car.)
3. Nisam siguran da ću uspeti da završim projekat u *predviđenom roku*. (I'm not sure I'll be able to finish the project within the expected timeframe.)
4. Naša firma ima *rok* od mesec dana da isporuči robu kupcima. (Our company has a deadline of one month to deliver the goods to customers.)
5. *Rok* za prijavljivanje na ovaj konkurs je sutra u ponoć. (The deadline for applying to this competition is tomorrow at midnight.)

I hope that helps!